    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in truly stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with maintenance, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
