    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This chassis has been meticulously inspected for subframe integrity and has received proactive rod bearing and Vanos solenoid service. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with firm bolsters and no pixel failure in the instrument cluster. Every electronic module is fully functional, and the engine bay remains in concours-level cleanliness. A mechanically flawless example for the serious collector.",
